SENTENCE of course part of what made this find so unusual is that the antikythera mechanism is constructed of bronze .
SENTENCE now ,  it is not that bronze was all that rare in greece then ,  it is just that bronze was valuable and could easily be recycled .
SENTENCE it would have been relatively easy for a person with knowledge of metals to melt down bronze objects and forge them into  ?
