SENTENCE now ,  it was a challenge to figure out the antikythera mechanism .
SENTENCE it spent over 2 ,     years at the bottom of the sea before it was discovered .
SENTENCE and even after it was discovered ,  it was still a number of years before we really understood what it was .
SENTENCE you see ,  the mechanism had corroded underwater ,  and many of the gears were stuck together in a mass .
SENTENCE cleaning it was only partly successful .
SENTENCE we could only get a good look at the structure of the gears after gamma rays were used to see inside ,  very similar to the way x rays are used to see your bones .
SENTENCE now ,  once we got a good look inside ,  we saw a really complex device .
SENTENCE the many gears not only moved in a way that could indicate the phases of the moon .
SENTENCE the antikythera mechanism also tracked both the lunar year and the solar year .
SENTENCE additionally ,  the gears also moved to match the motions of the planet and predicted eclipses .
SENTENCE but one thing that is particularly notable is that the mechanism was so precise that it even took into account a particular irregularity in the moon's orbit ,  which requires some very complex math to replicate in mechanical device .
SENTENCE you could say that the antikythera mechanism was a very precise calendar ,  which stands to reasons calendars were very important to ancient peoples .
SENTENCE religious festivals had to be held at the right time of year ,  crops needed to be planted at the right time as well .
SENTENCE and let's not forget that eclipses in planetary motions had important symbolic meanings .
